What is multipass?
--------------------

Multipassd is a daemon that orchestrates the creation, management and
maintenance of virtual machine and associated ubuntu images to simplify
development on various platforms such as OSX and Windows 10

Build Dependencies
---------------------------------------
    apt install devscripts equivs
    mk-build-deps -s sudo -i

Building
---------------------------------------
    cd <multipass>
    git submodule update --init --recursive
    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake ../
    make multipassd ubuntu

Running multipass daemon and client
---------------------------------------

   <multipass>/build/bin/multipassd &

   <multipass>/build/bin/ubuntu launch (a default qemu instance is launched)


Running the Electron app
---------------------------------------

    cd <multipass>/electron-app
    npm install
    npm start


Building a snap of the Electron app
---------------------------------------

    cd <multipass>/electron-app
    npm install
    npm run dist

The snap will end up in <multipass>/electron-app/dist/
